oi-build-firmware (0.6.6.6) asimov; urgency=low

  [Yauhen Kharuzhy]
  * Add v3ext flavour

  [Mikhail Gusarov]
  * Fixed v3ext nfsroot building
  * tmpfs for /tmp, /var/tmp, /var/log and /var/run, /var/lock
  * Send SIGHUP to madshelf, not SIGTERM - madshelf has grown the "reread
    directory" functionality.
  * X server no longer tries to listen on IPv6.
  * USB connect/disconnect handler added.
  * Fixed OI-on-SD rootfs mount race condition.
  * Added evdev to list of required modules.
  * Adapted to new X server (changed command-line arguments)
  * Added libextractor-oi-extras

